title: Karishma Kali Kaa
subTitle: A devout young woman is falsely accused of murdering a priest and absconding with the temple jewels. With her fate hanging in the balance, the woman seeks divine intervention to prove her innocence.

title: Prince
subTitle: A prince fakes his death to lead a simple life. He returns to the palace as a commoner only to learn that his father is dead and has left his young wife and her greedy brother in charge of the palace.

title: Ujala Hi Ujala
subTitle: Anuradha's stepmother forces her to consume alcohol and she becomes an addict. After her father's death, she takes over the business and falls in love with Vikram, but her happiness is short-lived.

title: Tarazu
subTitle: Ram Yadav, an honest police officer, earns the wrath of Appa Rao, an influential man, when he arrests the latter's criminal son.

title: Kyo Kii Main Jhuth Nahin Bolta
subTitle: Raj is a lawyer who finds great success with his countless fibs. However, when his son wishes for his father to stop lying, Raj is magically forced to speak the truth, which lands him in trouble.

title: Anjaam
subTitle: Vijay, a wealthy man, is in love with Shivani and is heartbroken when she gets married to Ashok. Unable to forget her, Vijay turns into a psychopath and tries to disrupt her marriage.

title: Rishtey
subTitle: A man marries his lover and has a child with her against the wishes of her wealthy father. However, his scheming father-in-law ruins their marriage and leaves to care for his boy by himself.

title: Hungama
subTitle: A millionaire businessman living in a village decides to move to the city with his wife. However, things take a comical turn as a case of mistaken identity causes chaos in their lives.

title: Yodha
subTitle: After he fails to save a hijacked flight, Arun, a soldier, is suspended. When he is found onboard another hijacked flight, his intentions are questioned.

title: Yodha
subTitle: After he fails to save a hijacked flight, Arun, a soldier, is suspended. When he is found onboard another hijacked flight, his intentions are questioned.

title: Patthar Ke Insan
subTitle: Talented sisters, Sita and Lata, are renowned performing artists. However, the rivalry between them leads to a competition with far-reaching consequences.

title: Dharam Adhikari
subTitle: Dharamraj, a righteous man, manages his village's affairs justly, making him well-liked among the people. Irked by his popularity, a jealous Chaudhury and Shastri conspire to get rid of him.

title: Veer
subTitle: Prithvi seeks revenge on Gyanendra Singh and the British. He sends his son Veer to Britain to study their plans. Veer kills Gyanendra's son but ends up falling in love with his daughter.

title: Aunty No. 1
subTitle: To help his friends, Gopi dresses up as their aunt to solve their problems. However, he gets into a hilarious situation where he must avoid two suitors trying to woo him.

title: Humko Tumse Pyaar Hai
subTitle: Durga, who is blind, loses her fiance, Rohit, while she is getting her eye surgery. As she copes with her pain, she finds solace in Raj but chaos ensues when Rohit returns from the dead.

title: Vinashak
subTitle: A diligent and determined police officer is tasked with uncovering the truth behind a crooked warden involved in illicit weapon trafficking.

title: Ziddi
subTitle: Deva, a vigilant young man, quickly climbs amongst the ranks of criminals in his city. However, things get complicated when he is framed for the assassination attempt of the CM.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Gupt
subTitle: After his stepfather is murdered, Sahil gets arrested but he manages to escape prison to prove his innocence. However, Inspector Udham Singh sets off to capture him.

title: Gang
subTitle: Four friends get together to start their career in crime and extortion and they succeed. However, things take a turn when one of them is arrested and sentenced for five years.

title: Inquilaab
subTitle: A politician helps a jobless man become a police officer and then uses him for his nefarious activities. After his wife finds out he is being used as a pawn, she tries to change his ways.

title: To Be Announced
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Jai Kishen
subTitle: Jai, a man who is visually impaired, discovers that he has a twin brother, Kishen, who was separated from him on the day his father was murdered. Thus, begins his quest for revenge with his sibling.

title: Sapne Saajan Ke
subTitle: Shalini, who has always wanted her daughter, Jyoti, to marry a rich man, is happy that she has found Deepak to be her life partner. However, no one knows that he is only pretending to be wealthy.

title: Garv: Pride and Honour
subTitle: An honest officer falls prey to a corrupt system where he is dismissed from the police force for getting involved in a murder case while trying to arrest a few corrupt politicians.

title: To Be Announced
subTitle: Bringing the best in television.

title: Sainik
subTitle: When Lieutenant Suraj goes missing, his father believes he is dead and decides to keep the news from his daughter and his son's wife. However, they already know and choose to put up a brave front.

title: Swarg
subTitle: Krishna worships his master, Sahabji, but circumstances lead to his ouster from the house. He works hard, becomes a powerful man and returns to restore his master's honour.

title: Zulmi
subTitle: Raj is hired as a bodyguard for Komal, and the two grow closer to each other over time. However, things get complicated when he comes across Nihal, the man who molested his sister.
